ed by Becky Albertalli</li>\n<li>Challenger Deep by Neal Shusterman</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mental Health in Young Adult Fiction","author":"Yashvini Deva","volume":17,"date":"September 13, 2020","topic":"Book Review","slug":"/ballot-buzz/v17a02"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ballot-buzz/v17a02"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}